## 8. APPENDICES

### Appendix A: Glossary

| Term | Definition |
|------|-----------|
| CVSS | Common Vulnerability Scoring System — standardized score for vulnerability severity |
| CWE | Common Weakness Enumeration — catalog of software security weakness types |
| CVE | Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures — public vulnerability identifiers |
| OWASP | Open Web Application Security Project |
| PTES | Penetration Testing Execution Standard |
| PoC | Proof of Concept — demonstration of vulnerability exploitability |
| RCE | Remote Code Execution |
| SSRF | Server-Side Request Forgery |
| XSS | Cross-Site Scripting |
| SQLi | SQL Injection |
| IDOR | Insecure Direct Object Reference |

